fields.calculatedFormula:
ABS(ROUND(12*(
(5*FLOOR((TODAY()-DATE(2007,01,01))/7) +
MIN(5, 
    MOD(TODAY()-DATE(2007,01,01), 7) +
    MIN(1, 24/12*(MOD(NOW()-DATETIMEVALUE('2007-01-01 17:00:00'), 1)))
))
-
(5*FLOOR((DATEVALUE( LastModifiedDate)-DATE(2007,01,01))/7) +
MIN(5, 
    MOD(DATEVALUE(LastModifiedDate)-DATE(2007,01,01), 7) +
    MIN(1, 24/12*(MOD(LastModifiedDate-DATETIMEVALUE('2007-01-01 17:00:00'), 1)))
))
), 0))
